## ðŸš€ Features
- **Search & Recommend:** Type any movie and get recommendations based on genres and categories.  
- **Netflix-Style UI:** Sleek, dark-themed, responsive layout with hover effects.  
- **Movie Posters:** Each movie comes with its official poster.  
- **Ratings & Reviews:** Quick ratings and brief reviews for each recommended movie.  
- **Dark/Light Mode Toggle:** Switch themes easily.  
- **Frontend-Only Deployment:** Powered by HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
- **Ready for Backend:** Can be extended later with Flask or Node.js for dynamic recommendations.

